===Noun===
'''needlework'''

# the art or process of working with a needle [[esp.]] in [[embroidery]] or [[needlepoint]] .
# the product of such art or process.
# the [[occupation]] or [[employment]] of a person skilled in [[embroidery]], [[needlepoint]], ect.

